01:12:02,359 --> 01:12:04,479
Come on. I'll show you my favorite place.

837
01:12:05,359 --> 01:12:06,199
Here.

838
01:12:35,239 --> 01:12:37,279
Do you like basketball that much?

839
01:12:41,000 --> 01:12:42,239
It's Neung's stuff.

840
01:12:42,880 --> 01:12:43,960
It's all old.

841
01:12:44,640 --> 01:12:45,920
Mine is in that box.

842
01:12:59,520 --> 01:13:01,479
I would like you to stay in my room,

843
01:13:01,560 --> 01:13:03,000
but it's small and messy.

844
01:13:03,079 --> 01:13:04,920
Stay in Neung's room instead.

845
01:13:05,399 --> 01:13:06,800
You look the same anyway.

846
01:13:22,560 --> 01:13:24,680
It will be like Neung still lives here.

847
01:13:27,760 --> 01:13:30,119
Yes, it will.

848
01:13:34,159 --> 01:13:35,399
Is the room okay?

849
01:13:36,600 --> 01:13:37,439
Yes.

850
01:13:39,359 --> 01:13:40,399
Wait a minute.

851
01:14:10,960 --> 01:14:12,960
Let's play games when you've had a shower.

852
01:14:13,920 --> 01:14:14,800
Okay.

853
01:14:42,680 --> 01:14:45,319
Am I really never
going to see Nut anymore?

854
01:14:55,840 --> 01:14:59,319
TOFU TOFU UPDATED HIS PROFILE PICTURE.

855
01:15:00,319 --> 01:15:05,439
TOFU: I MISS NUT.

856
01:15:48,720 --> 01:15:50,680
Why do I look like you?

857
01:15:55,239 --> 01:15:56,920
Why am I like this?

858
01:15:57,880 --> 01:15:59,319
What happened to me?

859
01:16:07,800 --> 01:16:10,039
I was Nut's teddy bear.

860
01:16:10,600 --> 01:16:12,560
Why did I become your look-alike?

861
01:16:16,439 --> 01:16:17,840
The person Nut loves…

862
01:16:23,479 --> 01:16:25,199
Who did this to me?

863
01:16:40,600 --> 01:16:42,840
Where can I find the answers?

864
01:17:35,720 --> 01:17:37,279
What are you doing, Dad?

865
01:17:43,439 --> 01:17:44,399
What is it?

866
01:17:44,920 --> 01:17:46,239
I saw someone.

867
01:17:46,800 --> 01:17:48,399
They're sneaking around outside.

868
01:17:50,560 --> 01:17:51,600
Is it a burglar?

869
01:17:52,359 --> 01:17:53,239
I don't know.

870
01:18:07,079 --> 01:18:07,920
Dad, wait.

871
01:18:19,359 --> 01:18:20,800
I'll catch the burglar.

872
01:18:20,880 --> 01:18:22,000
What?

873
01:18:22,760 --> 01:18:23,800
It's okay.

874
01:18:32,079 --> 01:18:33,119
Are you leaving?

875
01:18:37,720 --> 01:18:38,880
Did you come to see Tofu?

876
01:18:41,640 --> 01:18:42,640
Come inside.

877
01:18:55,680 --> 01:18:56,680
Thank you.

878
01:18:59,840 --> 01:19:01,039
You're Nut, aren't you?

879
01:19:04,640 --> 01:19:06,199
Song told me.

880
01:19:08,079 --> 01:19:09,039
Yes.

881
01:19:11,720 --> 01:19:13,800
Did you think it through
before coming here?

882
01:19:17,640 --> 01:19:19,880
Although Tofu has lost his memory,

883
01:19:20,600 --> 01:19:22,960
he still has feelings.

884
01:19:24,640 --> 01:19:26,520
You're not just his employer,

885
01:19:26,600 --> 01:19:28,479
and you didn't just save his life.

886
01:19:29,960 --> 01:19:32,119
You're his whole world,

887
01:19:32,880 --> 01:19:35,079
his sanctuary, and something to hang onto.

888
01:19:37,319 --> 01:19:41,119
If you take Tofu back, I only hope

889
01:19:42,239 --> 01:19:46,760
that he will get to stay with you
until his memory returns completely.

890
01:20:03,359 --> 01:20:04,600
Nut!

891
01:20:30,359 --> 01:20:32,079
Let's go home.

892
01:20:53,319 --> 01:20:55,159
Thank you, both of you.

893
01:20:57,439 --> 01:20:58,560
I'll get going now.

894
01:20:59,680 --> 01:21:00,560
Thank you.

895
01:21:03,239 --> 01:21:04,079
Let's go.

896
01:21:06,800 --> 01:21:07,640
Bye.

897
01:21:20,920 --> 01:21:22,319
Did we do the right thing?

898
01:21:22,880 --> 01:21:24,039
I don't know.

899
01:21:24,520 --> 01:21:27,479
But since they miss each other
and they want to stay together,

900
01:21:27,560 --> 01:21:28,760
we have to let them be.

901
01:21:29,880 --> 01:21:33,159
Now, we should go inside
and get some sleep.

902
01:21:33,239 --> 01:21:34,520
Are you sleepy?

903
01:21:34,600 --> 01:21:36,199
-I am.
-Go to bed then.

904
01:21:40,800 --> 01:21:42,279
I thought about the difference

905
01:21:43,439 --> 01:21:44,920
between not having you around,

906
01:21:46,159 --> 01:21:48,479
and having you despite being suspicious.

907
01:21:50,760 --> 01:21:52,399
Did you choose the latter?

908
01:21:53,399 --> 01:21:54,439
No.

909
01:21:55,600 --> 01:21:57,239
I just wanted to follow my heart.

910
01:21:58,319 --> 01:21:59,840
Whatever my heart wants,

911
01:21:59,920 --> 01:22:01,520
I want to let it be.

912
01:22:05,399 --> 01:22:06,960
Right now, I want to be with you.

913
01:22:10,720 --> 01:22:12,800
But I don't know
if I'll get paranoid again.

914
01:22:17,760 --> 01:22:19,359
I don't know what I need to do,

915
01:22:20,079 --> 01:22:21,920
but I want to move forward.

916
01:22:23,960 --> 01:22:25,600
I don't want to leave it hanging.

917
01:22:31,000 --> 01:22:32,520
Please be patient with me.

918
01:22:34,760 --> 01:22:36,920
I promise I'll never kick you out again.

919
01:22:38,960 --> 01:22:40,720
And I'll try not to mention him.

920
01:22:48,399 --> 01:22:50,239
I won't be able to forget him though.

921
01:22:51,880 --> 01:22:53,640
And I won't try to forget him…

922
01:22:57,359 --> 01:22:58,800
because our relationship

923
01:22:59,800 --> 01:23:02,720
is the happiest memory
I have from that time.

924
01:23:17,760 --> 01:23:19,840
But I won't force you to be him,…

925
01:23:21,760 --> 01:23:23,119
because you are you.

926
01:23:25,359 --> 01:23:27,039
He's in the past.

927
01:23:29,920 --> 01:23:31,439
But you're right here

928
01:23:32,399 --> 01:23:33,640
with me.

929
01:23:39,720 --> 01:23:41,119
I promise,

930
01:23:42,640 --> 01:23:44,359
I'll stay with you forever.

931
01:23:52,199 --> 01:23:53,399
Is that all?

932
01:23:55,359 --> 01:23:56,800
What more should I say?

933
01:23:58,600 --> 01:24:00,079
I gave a whole speech,

934
01:24:00,640 --> 01:24:02,000
and that's all you can say?

935
01:24:03,239 --> 01:24:05,159
I must look crazy.

936
01:24:15,960 --> 01:24:17,119
In that case,

937
01:24:18,600 --> 01:24:20,640
I'll try to be good.

938
01:24:22,560 --> 01:24:24,640
I'll be trustworthy,

939
01:24:25,479 --> 01:24:27,760
so that you can trust me,

940
01:24:29,760 --> 01:24:32,119
even though my identity

941
01:24:32,600 --> 01:24:34,520
might not seem so trustworthy.

942
01:24:36,439 --> 01:24:38,239
But everything I've done for you

943
01:24:39,479 --> 01:24:41,840
has always been sincere.

944
01:24:45,119 --> 01:24:46,520
One day,

945
01:24:47,800 --> 01:24:50,560
you'll recognize my sincerity.

946
01:24:52,560 --> 01:24:53,800
I'll prove it.

947
01:24:55,840 --> 01:24:57,079
I promise.

948
01:25:00,359 --> 01:25:01,920
Does that sound good?

949
01:25:04,119 --> 01:25:05,920
Okay. That's good.

950
01:25:07,039 --> 01:25:08,359
You promised.

951
01:25:08,960 --> 01:25:10,239
I'll wait and see.

952
01:25:18,800 --> 01:25:19,800
What now?

953
01:25:20,760 --> 01:25:23,640
This is how we promise.

954
01:25:25,520 --> 01:25:27,279
You're such a baby.

955
01:25:28,399 --> 01:25:31,319
This is how adults make a promise.

956
01:26:08,840 --> 01:26:10,079
Mom is probably asleep.

957
01:26:10,800 --> 01:26:12,119
We can tell her tomorrow.

958
01:26:30,520 --> 01:26:32,000
Welcome home.

959
01:26:41,439 --> 01:26:43,359
Tofu, hurry up.

960
01:26:44,319 --> 01:26:45,239
Okay.

961
01:27:00,479 --> 01:27:01,640
Good night.

962
01:27:02,199 --> 01:27:03,199
Wait.

963
01:27:07,279 --> 01:27:08,760
What is it?

964
01:27:09,479 --> 01:27:10,800
Did you forget something?

965
01:27:12,560 --> 01:27:13,680
What did I forget?

966
01:27:25,199 --> 01:27:26,159
This.

967
01:27:32,800 --> 01:27:34,159
What are you doing?

968
01:27:34,720 --> 01:27:36,399
I'm following your script.

969
01:27:37,760 --> 01:27:38,880
Shall we start?

970
01:27:48,239 --> 01:27:50,039
I'm not really feeling it.

971
01:27:53,960 --> 01:27:55,800
You're so hard to please.

972
01:27:58,119 --> 01:28:00,600
-We can rebuild the mood.
-Sure.

973
01:28:01,439 --> 01:28:03,439
Should we start from the angry part?

974
01:28:06,760 --> 01:28:08,439
Let's skip that.

975
01:28:09,000 --> 01:28:10,079
Then skip to your room.

976
01:28:11,039 --> 01:28:12,239
I'm not in the mood now.

977
01:28:15,000 --> 01:28:16,000
Nut.

978
01:28:16,840 --> 01:28:18,600
I'll skip forward for you.

979
01:28:19,560 --> 01:28:21,239
-Let's start at--
-Go.

980
01:28:22,479 --> 01:28:23,479
I'm going to bed.

981
01:29:05,560 --> 01:29:08,319
You've had him follow me
since we separated.

982
01:29:08,880 --> 01:29:10,319
Are you a psychopath?

983
01:29:10,399 --> 01:29:11,520
Why are you doing this?

984
01:29:12,119 --> 01:29:15,479
I'm doing all this because I love you.

985
01:29:15,560 --> 01:29:18,520
If I can't be happy, then no one will be.

986
01:29:18,600 --> 01:29:20,439
If I wasn't indecisive,

987
01:29:22,000 --> 01:29:23,680
if I had been firm

988
01:29:24,560 --> 01:29:27,319
I wouldn't have made the wrong choice.

989
01:29:27,399 --> 01:29:29,000
She didn't really love him.

990
01:29:29,079 --> 01:29:31,279
I'm just a product of their mistake.

991
01:29:32,319 --> 01:29:33,680
Am I supposed to give up

992
01:29:33,760 --> 01:29:35,720
and be a coward like you?

993
01:29:36,239 --> 01:29:38,279
And behave immorally like you?

994
01:29:38,840 --> 01:29:40,319
-I can't do it.
-Tarn!

995
01:29:42,359 --> 01:29:44,479
I already have plenty of friends.

996
01:29:45,560 --> 01:29:46,680
But now,

997
01:29:47,159 --> 01:29:48,560
I want you.

998
